Date: Thu, 5 Jun 2025 23:34:55 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 07/10] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL: hostapd: Add 6 GHz base regulatory
 APIs

Add new APIs to hostapd for 6 GHz base regulatory support.
  (1) Export the API 'hostapd_get_chan_width_from_oper_chan_width'
      to get the channel width from the operating channel width.
  (2) Add an API to get the best 6 GHz power mode for the iface.
  (3) Add an API to get the best 6 GHz power mode for the given
      freq, BW, puncture pattern.
  (4) Add APIs to validate if the given freq and BW can form an
      IEEE supported bonded channel.
  (5) Add an API to get the bonded channel's center frequency.
  (6) Use bonded channel's center frequency for getting the EIRP
      power for filling in the TPE IEs for each BW.

Fixes: None
Patch-work: None
Tag: 6G_REGULATORY
Feature: AFC
